      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one, and it still looks and smells like it just left the showroom! It's been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new and runs like a charm, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
