    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and aesthetic purity. This specimen features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, exhibiting factory-spec compression and zero evidence of thermal fatigue. The powerplant is mated to a crisp five-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Its four-wheel double-wishbone suspension remains tight, complementing the near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution for surgical turn-in. Finished in original Montego Blue with an immaculate interior, this unmolested example retains all factory heat shielding and vacuum line routing, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to own a definitive icon of the Golden Era.",
